* family ''[[Archasteridae|Archasteridae]]'' <small>Viguier, 1878</small>
* family ''[[Asterinidae|Asterinidae]]'' <small>Gray, 1840</small>
* family ''[[Asterodiscididae|Asterodiscididae]]'' <small>Rowe, 1977</small>
* family ''[[Asteropseidae|Asteropseidae]]'' <small>Hotchkiss & Clark, 1976</small>
